Pac-man

10 requirements

1.	The player must have option to start the game on the entrance screen

2.	The game must have walls that player canâ€™t go through

3.	The game must allow players to move in four direction (up, down, side to side)

4.	The game use the arrows on the keyboard as input

5.	The game must have small circle for player to collect as score

6.	The game must have one small circle as the power up upgrade

7.	The ghosts must be eatable by player when power up circle is consume

8.	The eatable ghost must be destroy after colliding with power up player

9.	After the ghost is destroy, the respawn time for the ghost should be 7 seconds

10.	The game must end when the player collect all small circle or all lives are gone

11.	The player must have 3 lives

